OL,3,C'Tired' Pep struggles to contain his
OL,4,Cemotions at Man City farewell
OL,6,FPep Guardiola admitted he was "so
OL,7,Ftired" and shed tears following his
OL,8,Ffinal game as Manchester City manager.
OL,10,FThe Spaniard bowed out after 10
OL,11,Fglorious years at the Etihad Stadium
OL,12,Ffollowing Sunday's Premier League
OL,13,Fdefeat against Aston Villa.
OL,15,FVilla did their best to spoil a
OL,16,Fcelebration of Guardiola's
OL,17,Fextraordinary achievements ` which
OL,18,Finclude the winning of 20 trophies `
OL,19,Fas they came from behind to claim a 2-
OL,20,F1 victory.
OL,26,@nD@_OUoD@FO]
