OL,3,C'Tired' Pep struggles to contain his
OL,4,Cemotions at Man City farewell
OL,6,FBut there was no doubting the occasion
OL,7,Fbelonged to Guardiola and two other
OL,8,Fstalwarts of his reign in Bernardo
OL,9,FSilva and John Stones, who made their
OL,10,Ffinal appearances.
OL,12,FGuardiola now intends to take a long
OL,13,Fbreak from the game but left no doubt
OL,14,Fthe club had made a big mark on him.
OL,16,FHe said: "I am so tired. Seriously, I
OL,17,Fam so tired. I did everything. We did
OL,18,Fit.
OL,26,@xD@JOU
