OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779700299
OL,3,C'Tired' Pep struggles to contain his
OL,4,Cemotions at Man City farewell
OL,6,F"The memories I have of Barcelona and
OL,7,FBayern Munich are unbeatable but the
OL,8,Fluggage of memories I have from here
OL,9,Ffrom 10 years is more than any other.
OL,11,F"Without the trophies I would have
OL,12,Fbeen sacked but it is not looking at
OL,13,Fthe trophies in the cabinet at home
OL,14,Fthat makes me happy.
OL,16,F"It is the memories and connections I
OL,17,Fhad since day one with the city, the
OL,18,Fbackroom staff and the players."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUzD@`O]
