PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779700299
OL,3,C'Tired' Pep struggles to contain his
OL,4,Cemotions at Man City farewell
OL,6,FGuardiola spoke on the pitch after the
OL,7,Fgame and admitted he struggled to keep
OL,8,Fhis emotions in check.
OL,10,FHe said: "I don't cry, but when I saw
OL,11,FBernardo cry I cried. I said don't cry
OL,12,Fbut it happened. It was such a special
OL,13,Fmoment. The emotions were so high. I
OL,14,Fwill never forget."
OL,16,FDespite the emotional send-off,
OL,17,FGuardiola had no doubt he was making
OL,18,Fthe right decision.
OL,26,@rD@JOUvD@SO]
