CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779700299
OL,3,C'Tired' Pep struggles to contain his
OL,4,Cemotions at Man City farewell
OL,6,FHe said: "It is the right time. I will
OL,7,Fnot miss it for a while, that's for
OL,8,Fsure. I feel deeply that the decision
OL,9,Fis the right decision for this club
OL,10,Fand the players. I thank the club for
OL,11,Frespecting it, they understood."
